TI  - Online (Remote) Teaching for Laboratory Based Courses Using "Digital Twins" of the Experiments
T2  - JOURNAL OF ENGINEERING FOR GAS TURBINES AND POWER-TRANSACTIONS OF THE ASME
LA  - English
