TI  - A Systematic Review of Digital Twin (DT) and Virtual Learning Environments (VLE) for Smart Manufacturing Education
T2  - MANUFACTURING LETTERS
LA  - English
KW  - Digital Twin (DT)
KW  - Virtual Learning Environment (VLE)
KW  - Manufacturing Education
KW  - Smart Manufacturing
KW  - Industry 5.0
