TI  - INTEGRATION OF ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE INTO THE TEACHING OF CHEMICAL TECHNOLOGY IN HIGHER EDUCATION: A SYSTEMATIC REVIEW
T2  - JOURNAL OF CHEMISTRY AND TECHNOLOGIES
LA  - Russian
