TI  - Emerging WEFE technologies in engineering education: Integration of optimization, explainable AI, digital twins, and virtual reality
T2  - ARRAY
LA  - English
KW  - Innovative technologies
KW  - WEFE nexus
KW  - Engineering education
KW  - Digital twins
KW  - Explainable AI (XAI)
